  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Season the cod fillets with salt, black pepper, and brazilian spices.",
    "Melt the butter in a ceramic tagine over medium heat.",
    "Add the beurre-monte and stir until well combined.",
    "Add the cod fillets and cook for 2 minutes on each side.",
    "Transfer the tagine to the preheated oven and bake for 12 minutes.",
    "Remove the tagine from the oven and sprinkle the icing sugar on top.",
    "Drizzle the lemon juice over the cod fillets and garnish with chopped parsley.",
    "Serve the flaky brazilian fish tagine hot and enjoy."
